snippet.title: Pizza Possum Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1951230/PIZZA_POSSUM/

Life is simple when you’re a possum. You love to steal food… all the food. And the world is your oyster. Except when you are hunted by guard dogs in an otherwise quiet and picturesque town. But that won’t stop you, so time for some arcade-style hide-and-seek action!
